  Locus:
    Page: 324
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - Miracles
---
To create miracles, you have to be very clear about what it is you want. By
acting forthright and acting as if you have already obtained the object or
condition that you desire, you create such a powerful energy that the
Universal Law gives you what you want.
